<div class="txtlevel"><p>Proiect de testare pentru studentii din grupa 231.</p></div>
 <br/><a name='toc_1'></a>
<h1 class='doclevel'>1.Test Suite : bpir3489_BBT</h1>
<div><p>Test suite for black-box testing of F01 &ndash; Add Product functionality.<br />
Test design techniques: Equivalence Class Partitioning (ECP) and Boundary Value Analysis (BVA).</p>
</div><a name="toc_tc27792"></a><p>&nbsp;</p><div> <table class="tc" width="90%" ><tr><th colspan="4">Test Case P231-1: TC_ECP_Valid_Add_Product&nbsp;<span style="font-size: 80%;">[Version  : 1]</span></th></tr>
<tr><td width="20%" valign="top"><span class="label">Author:</span></td><td colspan="3">bpir3489@scs.ubbcluj.ro</td></tr>
<tr><td colspan="4"><span class="label">Summary:</span><br /><p>Verify that a product can be successfully added when all input data is valid.</p>
</td></tr><tr><td colspan="4"><span class="label">Preconditions:</span><br /><p>The system is running and the user can access the Add Product functionality.</p>
</td></tr><tr><td><span class="label">#:</span></td><td><span class="label">Step actions:</span></td><td><span class="label">Expected Results:</span></td></tr><tr><td width="5">1</td><td><p>Enter valid product data (id, name, price, category, type) and execute the Add Product operation.</p>
</td><td><p>The product is successfully added to the system and appears in the product list.</p>
</td></tr><tr><td width="20%" valign="top"><span class="label">Execution type:</span></td><td colspan="3">Manual</td></tr>
<tr><td width="20%" valign="top"><span class="label">Estimated exec. duration (min):</span></td><td colspan="3"></td></tr>
<tr><td width="20%" valign="top"><span class="label">Importance:</span></td><td colspan="3">Medium</td></tr>
<tr><td colspan="4"></td></tr><tr><td > name of the autotest class:</td><td  colspan = "3" ></td></tr>
<tr><td > name of the test method:</td><td  colspan = "3" ></td></tr>
<tr><td width="20%" valign="top"><span class="label">Requirements</span><td colspan="3">bpir3489_F01:  F01_Add_Product [Version : 1]<br /></td></tr>
<tr><td width="20%" valign="top"><span class="label">Keywords:</span></td><td colspan="3">&nbsp;None<br/></td></tr>
</table>
</div>
<a name="toc_tc27795"></a><p>&nbsp;</p><div> <table class="tc" width="90%" ><tr><th colspan="4">Test Case P231-2: TC_ECP_Invalid_Add_Product&nbsp;<span style="font-size: 80%;">[Version  : 1]</span></th></tr>
<tr><td width="20%" valign="top"><span class="label">Author:</span></td><td colspan="3">bpir3489@scs.ubbcluj.ro</td></tr>
<tr><td colspan="4"><span class="label">Summary:</span><br /><p>Verify that the system rejects adding a product when invalid input data is provided.</p>
</td></tr><tr><td colspan="4"><span class="label">Preconditions:</span><br /><p>The system is running and the user can access the Add Product functionality.</p>
</td></tr><tr><td><span class="label">#:</span></td><td><span class="label">Step actions:</span></td><td><span class="label">Expected Results:</span></td></tr><tr><td width="5">1</td><td><p>Enter invalid product data (for example empty name or negative price) and execute the Add Product operation.</p>
</td><td><p>The system rejects the input and the product is not added to the system.</p>
</td></tr><tr><td width="20%" valign="top"><span class="label">Execution type:</span></td><td colspan="3">Manual</td></tr>
<tr><td width="20%" valign="top"><span class="label">Estimated exec. duration (min):</span></td><td colspan="3"></td></tr>
<tr><td width="20%" valign="top"><span class="label">Importance:</span></td><td colspan="3">Medium</td></tr>
<tr><td colspan="4"></td></tr><tr><td > name of the autotest class:</td><td  colspan = "3" ></td></tr>
<tr><td > name of the test method:</td><td  colspan = "3" ></td></tr>
<tr><td width="20%" valign="top"><span class="label">Requirements</span><td colspan="3">bpir3489_F01:  F01_Add_Product [Version : 1]<br /></td></tr>
<tr><td width="20%" valign="top"><span class="label">Keywords:</span></td><td colspan="3">&nbsp;None<br/></td></tr>
</table>
</div>
<a name="toc_tc27798"></a><p>&nbsp;</p><div> <table class="tc" width="90%" ><tr><th colspan="4">Test Case P231-3: TC_BVA_Valid_Add_Product&nbsp;<span style="font-size: 80%;">[Version  : 1]</span></th></tr>
<tr><td width="20%" valign="top"><span class="label">Author:</span></td><td colspan="3">bpir3489@scs.ubbcluj.ro</td></tr>
<tr><td colspan="4"><span class="label">Summary:</span><br /><p>Verify that a product can be added when the price is at the valid boundary value.</p>
</td></tr><tr><td colspan="4"><span class="label">Preconditions:</span><br /><p>The system is running and the user can access the Add Product functionality.</p>
</td></tr><tr><td><span class="label">#:</span></td><td><span class="label">Step actions:</span></td><td><span class="label">Expected Results:</span></td></tr><tr><td width="5">1</td><td><p>Enter product data where the price is at the minimum valid boundary value and execute the Add Product operation.</p>
</td><td><p>The product is successfully added to the system.</p>
</td></tr><tr><td width="20%" valign="top"><span class="label">Execution type:</span></td><td colspan="3">Manual</td></tr>
<tr><td width="20%" valign="top"><span class="label">Estimated exec. duration (min):</span></td><td colspan="3"></td></tr>
<tr><td width="20%" valign="top"><span class="label">Importance:</span></td><td colspan="3">Medium</td></tr>
<tr><td colspan="4"></td></tr><tr><td > name of the autotest class:</td><td  colspan = "3" ></td></tr>
<tr><td > name of the test method:</td><td  colspan = "3" ></td></tr>
<tr><td width="20%" valign="top"><span class="label">Requirements</span><td colspan="3">bpir3489_F01:  F01_Add_Product [Version : 1]<br /></td></tr>
<tr><td width="20%" valign="top"><span class="label">Keywords:</span></td><td colspan="3">&nbsp;None<br/></td></tr>
</table>
</div>
<a name="toc_tc27801"></a><p>&nbsp;</p><div> <table class="tc" width="90%" ><tr><th colspan="4">Test Case P231-4: TC_BVA_Invalid_Add_Product&nbsp;<span style="font-size: 80%;">[Version  : 1]</span></th></tr>
<tr><td width="20%" valign="top"><span class="label">Author:</span></td><td colspan="3">bpir3489@scs.ubbcluj.ro</td></tr>
<tr><td colspan="4"><span class="label">Summary:</span><br /><p>Verify that the system rejects adding a product when the price is below the minimum allowed boundary value.</p>
</td></tr><tr><td colspan="4"><span class="label">Preconditions:</span><br /><p>The system is running and the user can access the Add Product functionality.</p>
</td></tr><tr><td><span class="label">#:</span></td><td><span class="label">Step actions:</span></td><td><span class="label">Expected Results:</span></td></tr><tr><td width="5">1</td><td><p>Enter product data where the price is below the minimum allowed boundary value and execute the Add Product operation.</p>
</td><td><p>The system rejects the input and the product is not added to the system.</p>
</td></tr><tr><td width="5">2</td><td></td><td></td></tr><tr><td width="20%" valign="top"><span class="label">Execution type:</span></td><td colspan="3">Manual</td></tr>
<tr><td width="20%" valign="top"><span class="label">Estimated exec. duration (min):</span></td><td colspan="3"></td></tr>
<tr><td width="20%" valign="top"><span class="label">Importance:</span></td><td colspan="3">Medium</td></tr>
<tr><td colspan="4"></td></tr><tr><td > name of the autotest class:</td><td  colspan = "3" ></td></tr>
<tr><td > name of the test method:</td><td  colspan = "3" ></td></tr>
<tr><td width="20%" valign="top"><span class="label">Requirements</span><td colspan="3">bpir3489_F01:  F01_Add_Product [Version : 1]<br /></td></tr>
<tr><td width="20%" valign="top"><span class="label">Keywords:</span></td><td colspan="3">&nbsp;None<br/></td></tr>
</table>
